Pearl Thusi is now a student again! She posted the news on Twitter on Monday. Although she said she couldn't figure out how to apply for modules yet, she already has a student number. She registered with the University of South Africa (Unisa) and she sounds happy to be a student again. Pearl was previously a drama student at Wits University, but she paused her studies for her career in the entertainment industry.  Earlier, she posted about how she was struggling with the application.   